UPnP Router Control
******************************************

Copyright (C) 2009  Daniele Napolitano <dnax88@gmail.com>

A UPnP port mapper for routers that support it


Compilation and installation
============================

In order to compile UPnP Port Mapper you need following software packages:
	- GTK+ library ( >= 2.16 )
	- GUPnP library

To configure run:
	./waf configure --prefix=/usr
 
Configure automatically searches for all required components and packages. 

To compile and install run:
	./waf build
	sudo ./waf install


Information
===========

Main project site:
	https://launchpad.net/upnp-router-control

